title: MidPoint Indie Summer Series
text:
MidPoint Indie Summer Series is an annual event held at <a href="Fountain%20Square%2C%20Cincinnati">Fountain Square</a> in <a href="Cincinnati%2C%20Ohio">Cincinnati, Ohio</a> hosted by <a href="MidPoint%20Music%20Festival">MidPoint Music Festival</a>. The series showcases artists from around the world every Friday from 7–11 pm during the summer. As the name suggests, it highlights <a href="Indie%20Rock">Indie Rock</a> music but also displays other genres like <a href="rock%20music">Rock</a>, <a href="pop%20music">Pop</a>, and <a href="Folk%20music">Folk</a> music.
